                            <comment id="13229351" author="ratha" created="Wed, 14 Mar 2012 17:04:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;attaching the patch, please review and commit&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13714174" author="hiranya" created="Fri, 19 Jul 2013 22:33:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out. The CopyOnWriteArrayList seems to be costly. It duplicates the underlying array on each write. I fixed the issue by using a ConcurrentLinkedQueue instead, which uses a more efficient wait-free synchronization algorithm.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
